sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant H as Handler
    participant M as Manager
    participant R as Redis
    participant Recv as Receiver
    C->>H: POST /events/abc + body
    H->>R: EVALSHA append.lua — durable append · handler.go
    H-->>C: 204 · Stream-Next-Offset
    H->>M: OnStreamAppend(events/abc) · handler.go
    M->>R: SMEMBERS ds:{__ds}:stream:abc — fan-out
    M->>R: EVALSHA arm_wake.lua — generation++, ZADD lease · manager.go
    Note over M: idle → waking · mint wake_id
    M->>Recv: POST webhook · Webhook-Signature t,kid,ed25519
    Recv-->>M: 200 {done:true}
    M->>R: EVALSHA ack.lua — fence · ack tail · release · manager.go
    Note over R: cursor → tail · waking → idle
